	<center>
		<h1>Introduction</h1>
		<hr>
	</center>
        <p>I worked on expanding transcript support for the VC by implementing the following features:</p>
	<ul>
            <li>A transcript parser</li>
            <li>A transcript converter</li>
            <li>XML-formatted transcript import</li>
            <li>XML-formatted transcript export</li>
            <li>Indexing support for imported transcripts</li>
	</ul>
        <p>We have integrated Jim's indexing support and Beatriz's yellow pages database into the VC with Chris's FaceAlive implementation.</p>
